                                 INTRODUCTION
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Welcome  to  Smart  Cardz PD - a NON AGA conversion of Klondike deluxe for all
Amiga owners to use.  Smart Cardz retains one of the best features of
@{"Klondike Deluxe" link "distribution"} i.e. the ability to load other @{"card sets" link "other_sets"} . 


